45
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,979
<i>She's a celebrity pregnant woman. I do not recognize her.</i>

46
00:03:35,979 --> 00:03:38,540
<i>She seems is a little angry.</i>

47
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:43,999
