50
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:51,719
I chose Anxing Hospital because it can protect the privacy of its patients.

51
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:56,010
And for my privacy, we've signed an extra special contract.

52
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:57,719
Miss Ji, don't worry.

53
00:03:57,720 --> 00:04:01,099
Our hospital will protect our patients' privacy just like usual.

54
00:04:01,099 --> 00:04:04,432
But shooting in the hospital, so many people will be involved.

55
00:04:04,433 --> 00:04:07,840
Now anyone can post anything on the internet.

56
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,019
How can I rest assured?

57
00:04:10,019 --> 00:04:13,800
Besides, in case something goes wrong,

58
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:16,139
you can't do anything. Right?

59
00:04:16,139 --> 00:04:19,950
And I have my own plan going public.

60
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:22,200
Miss Ji, I also understand your concerns.

61
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,980
If you really can't accept it,

62
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:27,600
I can arrange to change you to a partnering hospital.

63
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,759
Is that okay for you?

64
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,699
