78
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:24,030
That movie made me cry a lot.

79
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,118
It was released ten years ago.

80
00:05:27,119 --> 00:05:29,979
And last year, the drama, "Rose Garden,"

81
00:05:29,979 --> 00:05:33,740
I remember it ranked No.1 in viewer ratings, right?

82
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:35,640
That's right!

83
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,420
So happy you liked it.

84
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:41,359
Miss Ji, later, would you mind giving me an autograph?

85
00:05:41,359 --> 00:05:42,599
I can do it for you.

86
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,040
Thanks a lot.

87
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,940
I've been a big fan of yours for a long time.

88
00:05:53,500 --> 00:06:00,200
President Lu, about the documentary, please give me, a VVIP, a satisfying reply, as soon as possible.

89
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,019
No problem

90
00:06:03,079 --> 00:06:04,660
Looking forward to your upcoming movies.

91
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:06,179
Goodbye.

92
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,679
Are you really a big fan of hers?

93
00:06:18,679 --> 00:06:19,900
Of course not.

94
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:22,899
When I read through important documents, her information was in them.

95
00:06:22,899 --> 00:06:25,439
So I just kept them in mind.

96
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:27,700
You are a great actress.

97
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:29,958
This is what Deputy Director taught me.

98
00:06:29,959 --> 00:06:32,339
There must be skill in speaking and doing things.

99
