102
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:43,238
and praised for her good acting skills, popularity, and professionalism.

103
00:06:43,239 --> 00:06:45,039
Of course she'd be happy.

104
00:06:46,859 --> 00:06:50,679
Why didn't I notice that you were so clever?

105
00:06:50,679 --> 00:06:53,759
You thought I was stupid?

106
00:06:54,859 --> 00:06:57,859
Who regarded me as a medicinal liquor seller?

107
00:06:58,540 --> 00:07:01,299
About what happened before, we agreed to forget it all.

108
00:07:01,299 --> 00:07:03,660
So I can't mention it anymore?

109
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:14,660
Working with you, if I'm not smart, I'll be in big trouble.

110
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:21,400
About Miss Ji, what's your plan?

111
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,560
No plan.

112
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,380
As she is pregnant, I don't want her to be angry.

113
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,540
Or I would have rejected her directly.

114
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:33,139
By the original plan to make the documentary, they are supposed to talk with the pregnant mothers next week.

115
00:07:33,139 --> 00:07:36,900
It's most likely that someone secretly got the word out.

116
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,520
That's okay.

117
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:42,410
I hate being led by the nose by others.

118
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,859
Do you have other concerns?

119
00:07:53,679 --> 00:07:55,779
Now, Director Zhang is involved.

120
00:07:55,779 --> 00:07:59,978
Asking Miss Ji to make trouble won't be all that they want. It won't be so simple.

121
00:07:59,978 --> 00:08:01,279
So?

122
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:03,118
When you were appointed to be president,

123
00:08:03,119 --> 00:08:04,558
