131
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:29,200
Don't worry.

132
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:31,993
Just carry out the documentary schedule as was our original plan.

133
00:08:31,993 --> 00:08:33,459
Okay.

134
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,860
