155
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:51,179
I don't know that.

156
00:09:51,179 --> 00:09:53,080
Chief Huang.

157
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:55,400
Okay.

158
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:58,699
- What's wrong?
- It's Ye Shilan's mother.

159
00:09:58,699 --> 00:10:00,478
This is Chief Huang of Pediatrics.

160
00:10:00,479 --> 00:10:03,619
If you have any questions, he can answer you.

161
00:10:03,619 --> 00:10:05,899
Hello, Chief Huang.

162
00:10:05,899 --> 00:10:07,399
About Ye Shilan's position,

163
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:10,279
right now, she's only working as an assistant temporarily.

164
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:13,320
Later, she'll be back to Pediatrics.

165
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,639
That's great.

166
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:18,830
Thanks, Chief Huang, please take care of Lanlan.

167
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,639
Yeah, of course.

168
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:21,839
Right.

169
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:25,319
These are some pecans I brought here from my hometown.

170
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,439
I originally wanted Lanlan to give them to you.

171
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:30,460
Now I have met you here, please accept them.

172
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:31,558
It's a small gift.

173
00:10:31,559 --> 00:10:33,659
Well. Okay.

174
00:10:33,659 --> 00:10:35,439
It's a small gift.

175
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,059
I won't reject it.

176
00:10:37,059 --> 00:10:39,179
Zhang, please put this here.

177
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:42,560
I'll get it later. I'll share them with her colleagues.

178
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,678
Yeah, great.

179
00:10:43,679 --> 00:10:45,000
I have to go back to work.

180
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,420
Thanks.

181
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:02,359
President Lu, is it okay for me to leave earlier today? For personal reasons.

182
00:11:02,359 --> 00:11:03,860
Okay, we can get downstairs together.

183
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:05,320
Thanks.

184
00:11:07,839 --> 00:11:09,479
Let's go.

185
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:38,080
<i>It's not like we're a couple.</i>

186
00:11:43,220 --> 00:11:44,759
<i>Sorry.</i>

187
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:47,840
<i>My mom... She...</i>

188
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:56,839
<i>Mom, it was taken several days ago,</i>

189
00:11:56,839 --> 00:12:01,200
<i> when he was tired from work. Taken during a break.</i>

190
00:12:09,939 --> 00:12:11,640
It's dirty.

191
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,320
Please.

192
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:37,240
<i>They will see each other.</i>

193
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:40,900
<i>Shall I tell the truth?</i>

194
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:43,840
President Lu.

195
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:49,278
Would you mind going back to work for a while?

196
00:12:49,278 --> 00:12:52,380
What? Do you think that I'm not working hard?

197
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:54,259
No.

198
00:12:54,259 --> 00:12:58,859
I just think that I'm not in the office, what if someone comes to visit you?

199
00:12:58,859 --> 00:13:01,139
I already have plans with Assistant Lin.

200
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:21,420
President Lu, do you need to go to the restroom?

201
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,619
I'm worried that there will be heavy traffic.

202
00:13:26,619 --> 00:13:28,760
A full bladder is not good for your health.

203
00:13:29,459 --> 00:13:32,499
