204
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:35,420
Addicted to being a doctor?

205
00:13:39,259 --> 00:13:42,180
Please don't meet my mom. Please don't meet my mom.

206
00:14:00,019 --> 00:14:02,279
- Lanlan.
- Mom.

207
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:04,032
Mom, where did you go?

208
00:14:04,032 --> 00:14:06,373
I went to the restroom.

209
00:14:06,373 --> 00:14:08,079
What brings you here?

210
00:14:08,079 --> 00:14:09,659
Wei's mom is at the hospital. Everything is okay.

211
00:14:09,659 --> 00:14:12,860
And it's not far from your hospital, so I came to see you.

212
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,499
Do you need to go back?

213
00:14:14,499 --> 00:14:16,280
No. Wei is taking care of her.

214
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:19,039
I'll take his shift tomorrow morning.

215
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:20,619
- Let me take it.
- It's okay.

216
00:14:20,619 --> 00:14:21,920
- Are you tired?
- Not at all.

217
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:24,698
I want to stay with you tonight. Is that okay?

218
00:14:24,698 --> 00:14:26,440
Of course.

219
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:28,592
Well. I'll call a taxi.

220
00:14:28,592 --> 00:14:30,419
- We can go home now.
- No.

221
00:14:30,419 --> 00:14:32,900
I remember you said before, there's a direct bus.

222
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:35,760
It's okay to take a bus.

223
00:14:37,019 --> 00:14:40,358
Fine. And I think we can have a seat on the bus now.

224
00:14:40,358 --> 00:14:43,099
- Let's go home.
- Let's go.

225
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:44,999
I see that you've lost weight again.

226
00:14:44,999 --> 00:14:47,159
No. I eat a lot every day.

227
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:49,199
Tonight, I'll cook some delicious dishes for you.

228
00:14:49,199 --> 00:14:50,740
Great.

229
00:14:53,459 --> 00:14:56,800
Lanlan, the environment of your hospital is really nice.

230
00:14:56,800 --> 00:15:00,252
Not many patients. Everyone is so friendly.

231
00:15:00,252 --> 00:15:01,679
Not like others.

232
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:03,152
So many patients.

233
00:15:03,152 --> 00:15:05,439
Doctors are so busy, just like they are in a war.

234
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,840
They are so hard-working.

235
00:15:07,719 --> 00:15:12,119
We are a high-end private hospital, with high fees and good service.

236
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:22,318
You transferred to an assistant. Why didn't you tell me?

237
00:15:24,300 --> 00:15:26,740
I didn't want you to be worried.

238
00:15:26,740 --> 00:15:28,578
And it's temporary.

239
00:15:28,578 --> 00:15:31,620
Later, I'll go back to Pediatrics.

240
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:36,650
I met Chief Huang at the reception area.

241
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:38,399
What did he tell you?

242
00:15:38,399 --> 00:15:41,410
He said you would go back to Pediatrics soon.

243
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:46,059
And I sent him pecans, hoping that he could support you.

244
00:15:50,619 --> 00:15:56,159
Lanlan, you're just like your dad; very straightforward.

245
00:15:56,159 --> 00:16:00,360
Now you're working, you should learn more social skills.

246
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,818
Don't just follow your ideas.

247
00:16:02,818 --> 00:16:05,079
It's not easy to work here.

248
00:16:05,079 --> 00:16:07,990
Learn how to get on well with your leader.

249
00:16:07,990 --> 00:16:09,530
Follow the order.

250
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:12,430
Or you won't get any benefits in the end.

251
00:16:12,439 --> 00:16:16,119
Mom, you've said it a lot of times.

252
00:16:16,119 --> 00:16:17,899
- Okay.
- You talked my ear off.

253
00:16:17,899 --> 00:16:19,819
Okay, fine.

254
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:25,919
Well. Have you told your boyfriend that I was here?

255
00:16:29,019 --> 00:16:32,679
He went on a business trip for several days.

256
00:16:33,179 --> 00:16:35,660
Such a coincidence?

257
00:16:36,220 --> 00:16:38,060
Yeah.

258
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:40,900
